    <h1>Map Pack</h1>
    <p class="description">The block of 3 local business listings that appears at the top of Google for local-intent searches. Also called the <strong>Local Pack or Google 3-Pack</strong>. Draws <strong>42% of all local search clicks</strong> — it is the highest-value position in local SEO.</p>
