            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Map Pack placement is earned through relevance, distance, and prominence signals — not direct payment. Local Services Ads appear above the Map Pack as a paid format, but they are separate from organic Map Pack listings.</p></div></div>
